  }, "v26"), mdx("p", null, "Khi l\xFAa m\xEC n\u1EA9y m\u1EA7m v\xE0 b\u1EAFt \u0111\u1EA7u sinh h\u1ED9t, th\xEC c\u1ECF d\u1EA1i c\u0169ng xu\u1EA5t hi\u1EC7n. "), mdx("h6", {
